name: Global X ReSolve Adaptive Asset Allocation Corporate Class ETF
longDescription: Horizons HRAA may invest in instruments that provide exposure to both domestic and foreign markets, including emerging markets. Horizons HRAA will also hold a large portion of its assets in cash, money market mutual funds, U.S. treasury securities, or other cash equivalents, some or all of which will serve as margin or collateral for Horizons HRAAs investments. Horizons HRAA seeks longterm capital appreciation by investing, directly or indirectly, in major global asset classes including but not limited to equity indexes, fixed income indexes, interest rates, commodities and currencies.
